          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Alternate game -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Successfully complete the game and wait until the credits end. Save the game, then continue from the saved game. You will be given a choice of which sword to use after each level in the alternate game. Successfully complete the game two times and wait until the credits end. Save the game, then continue from the saved game. The game will allow various areas in each level to be selected.</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
